| [3/4 ct H-I/SI1-SI2](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/bezel-diamond-pendant-in-14k-yellow-gold-3-4-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251417?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) | $3,460 | 7 | Shop |
