> **Farzana's Expert Take:** The bezel is the right choice for active wearers — anyone who exercises, does hands-on work, or wants a pendant they can forget they're wearing. No prongs to snag, no risk of the stone tilting. The ½ct at $2,100 is the most practical size for daily wear — visible without being heavy.

