## Halo Diamond Pendants: 2 Reviews, 15% Off

The halo setting surrounds the center diamond with a circle of smaller pavé-set diamonds. The effect is a significantly larger visual presence for the carat weight — a ½ct center stone in a halo looks comparable in size to a ¾ct solitaire. The trade-off: more diamonds means more maintenance (pavé stones can loosen over time) and a busier look than a clean solitaire.

